flowchart TB
    U[Recruiter / HR UI / Admin UI]
    API[FastAPI API Gateway<br/>Auth RBAC Request Validation]
    ORCH[Workflow Orchestrator<br/>Temporal]
    DB[(PostgreSQL<br/>system of record)]
    OBJ[(S3 / MinIO<br/>binary storage)]
    VDB[(pgvector or Qdrant<br/>vector storage)]
    CACHE[(Redis<br/>cache / locks / rate limits)]
    OBS[Observability<br/>OpenTelemetry + Logs + Metrics]
    PDF[Report Renderer<br/>HTML templates + WeasyPrint]
    LLM[LLM / Agent Workers<br/>LangGraph or internal agent runtime]
    PARSE[Document Processing Service<br/>Docling / Unstructured / OCR if needed]
    BG[Background Check Service<br/>policy-controlled integrations]
    RULES[Deterministic Scoring / Policy Engine]
    SEARCH[Evidence Retrieval Service]
    NOTIFY[Notifications / Webhooks]

    U --> API
    API --> DB
    API --> OBJ
    API --> ORCH
    API --> CACHE

    ORCH --> DB
    ORCH --> OBJ
    ORCH --> PARSE
    ORCH --> LLM
    ORCH --> SEARCH
    ORCH --> BG
    ORCH --> RULES
    ORCH --> PDF
    ORCH --> NOTIFY

    PARSE --> OBJ
    PARSE --> DB
    PARSE --> VDB

    LLM --> DB
    LLM --> OBJ
    LLM --> VDB

    SEARCH --> VDB
    SEARCH --> DB
    SEARCH --> OBJ

    BG --> DB
    BG --> OBJ

    RULES --> DB
    PDF --> OBJ
    PDF --> DB

    API --> OBS
    ORCH --> OBS
    PARSE --> OBS
    LLM --> OBS
    BG --> OBS
    RULES --> OBS
    PDF --> OBS